-- LG Display to Form Venture in China with Iriver to Make Electronic Books
-- Saeromi Shin
-- 2010-06-14T02:46:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-14/lg-display-to-form-venture-in-china-with-iriver-to-make-electronic-books.html

          
          
             LG Display Co. said it will form a
venture with Iriver Ltd. to produce electronic books in China.  
 The plan is subject to Chinese government approval, LG
Display said in a regulatory filing today.  
